        <section id="detailed_desc">
            <p>Use this method to monitor the plugging and swapping of external audio or video devices, for example, an external camera. </p>
            <note id="note_v4j_tbx_jqb" type="attention" props="windows">
                <p>This method is for macOS only.</p>
            </note>
        </section>
        <section id="parameters"><title>Parameters</title>     
   <parml>
       <plentry>
           <pt>enabled</pt>
  <pd>Whether to monitor the change of the device state:<ul id="ul_qjq_swq_t4b">
 <li><codeph><ph keyref="true"/></codeph>: Monitor the device state change.</li>
 <li><codeph><ph keyref="false"/></codeph>: Do not monitor the device state change.</li>
      </ul></pd>
       </plentry>
   </parml>
        </section>
